What is the purpose of the "Applied Steps" pane in Power Query?
  View the result at that stage.
  Edit the transformation (e.g., change a filter or column name).
  Delete or reorder steps to change the logic of your data prep.
How do you remove duplicate rows in Power Query?
  Go to the Home tab > Click Remove Rows > Choose Remove Duplicates.
What does the "Filter" icon do in Power Query?
  The filter icon appears next to each column header.
  Clicking it lets you choose which values to keep or remove from that column.
How would you rename a column from "CustID" to "CustomerID"?
  left click and  search rename
What happens if you click "Close & Apply" in Power Query?
  changes are stored 
